io.jstach.kiwi.boot
A Opinionated loading of configuration using Kiwi KVS based on Spring Boot loading style.
  • Classes in io.jstach.kiwi.boot used by io.jstach.kiwi.boot
    Class
    Description
    KiwiConfig
    Kiwi Config is tiny opinionated configuration framework modeled after Spring Boot that uses Kiwi KVS system to load key values into a Map.
    KiwiConfig.ReloadableConfig
    A reloadable config allows reloading but does not guarantee that repeated calls of KiwiConfig.getProperty(String) and similar will return the same results.
    KiwiConfig.StableConfig
    A stable config guarantees that repeated calls of KiwiConfig.getProperty(String) and similar will return the same result.
